metadata.description:
After months and months of teasing, "Kaleidoscope (Me&U)" is finally here.

I'm so happy of this record, and I couldn't have made it without the one and only Alexander Lewis, whom I actually met through Sound early this year!
This song feels like a breath of fresh air to me, and marks the start of a new era for my music.
Hope you'll enjoy it.

Much love,
camo
